Installation :
    git clone --recursive git://github.com/tejovanthn/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks :
    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Update submodules:
    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Install submodules:
    git submodule add git://github.com/tpope/vim-fugitive.git bundle/vim-fugitive
    git commit -m 'Added vim-fugitive'
    git push
